Danieli Logo Danieli Group is an Italian supplier of equipment and physical plants to the metal industry. The company is based in Buttrio, in the north-east of Italy. It is one of the world leaders in the production of steel plants, in particular in the long products segment, where it owns more than a 90% market share. It has more than 25 divisions worldwide, 7 of which are Production Centers. Source
